rl=https://topick.hket.com/article/1710627/%E4%BF%9D%E8%89%AF%E5%B1%80%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E7%87%9F%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%91%91%E7%BD%B0%E8%B7%AA%E5%9C%B0%20%20%20%20%20%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%B3%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%EF%BC%9A%E5%A5%BD%E4%BC%BC%E5%85%A5%E5%92%97%E9%82%AA%E6%95%99|title=保良局訓練營學生被摑罰跪地 受害學生：好似入咗邪教|author=香港經濟日報|date=2017-03-16|accessdate=2017-11-07|archive-date=2020-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110145246/https://topick.hket.com/article/1710627/%E4%BF%9D%E8%89%AF%E5%B1%80%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E7%87%9F%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%91%91%E7%BD%B0%E8%B7%AA%E5%9C%B0%20%20%20%20%20%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%B3%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%EF%BC%9A%E5%A5%BD%E4%BC%BC%E5%85%A5%E5%92%97%E9%82%AA%E6%95%99|dead-url=no}}{{zh-hk}}</ref>，保良局在最後為了保持聲譽遂與訓練營承辦商解約<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/882510/|title=保良局與訓練營承辦商解約　暫停辦訓練營保聲譽|author=頭條新聞|date=2017-04-14|accessdate=2017-11-07|archive-date=2017-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107222548/http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/882510/|dead-url=no}}{{zh-hk}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170414/bkn-20170414101659051-0414_00822_001.html|title=涉粗暴對待學生　保良局與訓練營承辦商解約|author=ON.CC東網|date=2017-04-14|accessdate=2017-11-07|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128021319/http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170414/bkn-20170414101659051-0414_00822_001.html|dead-url=no}}{{zh-hk}}</ref>，事件暫告一段落。

